This folder contains all the projects made while learning about risc-v

7-16-2026 calculator_with_ff 12:30 - created a calculator with one of the input as the previous value of the output using flip flop 
                                     to simulate a real calculator where the new calculation is done on the previous output. Rum this
                                     code in makerchip.

7-17-2026 risc_v_initial     12:48 - started working on the risc v. Started with the program counter, added the logic that will make
                                     it increment with each clock cycle to go to the next instruction starting from 0.
                             13:00 - Added the IMEM part which holds the instruction set. It has been connected to the PC.

